Subject: net: Added pointer check for dst->ops->neigh_lookup in
 dst_neigh_lookup_skb
Git-commit: 394de110a73395de2ca4516b0de435e91b11b604
Patch-mainline: 5.8-rc5
References: networking-stable-20_07_17

The packets from tunnel devices (eg bareudp) may have only
metadata in the dst pointer of skb. Hence a pointer check of
neigh_lookup is needed in dst_neigh_lookup_skb

Kernel crashes when packets from bareudp device is processed in
the kernel neighbour subsytem.

